lt;a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Ff545448\"&gt;</ph>Driver Verifier<ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph> on the test computer.","pos":[20691,20818],"source":"Disables <a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Ff545448\">Driver Verifier</a> on the test computer."},{"content":"Parameters:<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ph> None","pos":[20834,20859],"source":"Parameters:</strong> None"},{"content":"Enable Driver Verifier","pos":[21036,21058]},{"content":"You can use this test to enable <ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Ff545448\"&gt;</ph>Driver Verifier<ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph> for all drivers of a device (or devices) on the test computer.","pos":[21088,21279],"source":"You can use this test to enable <a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Ff545448\">Driver Verifier</a> for all drivers of a device (or devices) on the test computer."},{"content":"Parameters:<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;/strong&gt; -</ph> See <ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Ff545448_options\"&gt;</ph>Driver Verifier Options<ph id=\"ph3\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph>.","pos":[21295,21435],"source":"Parameters:</strong> - See <a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Ff545448_options\">Driver Verifier Options</a>."},{"content":"Related topics","pos":[21506,21520],"source":"Related topics\n"},{"content":"How to How to test a driver at runtime using Visual Studio","pos":[21573,21631]},{"content":"Device Fundamentals Tests","pos":[21668,21693]},{"content":"Provided WDTF Simple I/O plug-ins","pos":[21766,21799]},{"content":"How to customize I/O for your device using the WDTF Simple I/O Action Plug-in","pos":[21872,21949]},{"pos":[22025,23007],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Send comments about this topic to Microsoft<ept id=\"p1\">]</ept><bpt id=\"p2\">(mailto:wsddocfb@microsoft.com?subject=Documentation%20feedbac